Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,Brotherhood
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 25
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,===============================================================

Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:34.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Anyone here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:38.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Al!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:41.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:43.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:44.83,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:46.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:48.21,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:51.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:53.80,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Is that any way to speak to a prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.37,0:01:55.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:01:59.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:01.05,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:04.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're not actually Envy disguised as Lin, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:05.80,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:09.74,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to recite the entire room service menu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.74,0:02:11.15,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you're not fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:15.36,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a fake either, are you? You pea--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:18.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a pea-sized runt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:19.82,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:26.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But seriously, where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:32.96,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, we were swallowed up by Gluttony, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:37.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but there's no way his stomach could be this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:38.57,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.26,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:44.78,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,It's the deserted house we were just in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.14,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,And this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:50.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The Lieutenant's car?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:54.02,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's safe to assume that all this fire came from the Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:55.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:58.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:01.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...we're really inside Gluttony's stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:02.42,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:05.94,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,But I can at least tell you we're not in Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:07.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:08.37,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:14.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:16.88,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Al's?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:21.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If we can only find his arm,\Nthat means Al wasn't swallowed with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:23.89,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:27.78,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Al is worried sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:31.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We've got no idea where we are, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:37.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the perfect time for them to awaken!\NMy telepathic abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:40.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Elric telepathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:42.91,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hear me, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:42.62,Default-alt,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:52.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I see a lot of buildings and corpses,\Nbut they're all from different times...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:55.84,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Is there even an exit to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:58.20,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. And if there isn't, I'll make one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:04:00.62,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,And where are you going to make one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:05.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,All right, throw that stick in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:06.93,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I see what you're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:08.47,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:19.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's hit the bottom yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:21.44,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,A wall! Let's look for a wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:26.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! No matter how big the place is, we'll eventually reach the edge if we just keep moving forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:29.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We should be able to find the exit, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.04,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:40.12,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go, Shao May?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:43.09,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it got eaten up by a stray dog or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.33,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,A stray?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.35,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,That was a joke! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:50.35,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:56.33,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Shao May is a panda who has had a minor disorder since birth, which prevented her from getting any bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:05:00.36,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I found her after she was abandoned by her parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:04.22,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,...and we've been raised like sisters ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:13.87,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,My clan, the Chang, barely has any authority in Xing, making us one of the weakest clans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.45,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:24.21,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,How can I put it... we were both attracted to each other because of our similar standings...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:29.64,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It may have been sympathy at first...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:46.74,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,...but we were raised like family, carried the same burdens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:51.97,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,...and she eventually became someone irreplaceable to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:06:00.84,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of things I was able to go through, just because she was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:05.22,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have been able to cross the desert without her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:07.97,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you really had to cross it in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:12.89,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do all this for something uncertain like immortality?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:19.05,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't bring back the method of immortality...\NIf I don't present it to the Emperor and earn his favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:22.22,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,My clan will die out at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:26.36,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I came here with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:27.79,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,With her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:32.02,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Shao May!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:32.02,Default-alt,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:43.49,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:46.13,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,We still have some time before the sun rises.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.81,0:06:49.33,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be alot of military police on-duty at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:49.96,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:53.85,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,You'll help me look for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:57.95,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:02.44,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,His people died out in that civil war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:10.33,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,So maybe he's empathizing with you and your weak clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:15.28,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Aren't you going to look for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:17.70,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:28.38,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Having to walk in all this really drains your stamina, doesn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:33.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And no signs of an exit, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:36.25,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:43.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If we manage to get out, I'll let you eat all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:48.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Eat all you want, sleep all you want, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:51.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:54.53,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:57.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, giving up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:02.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You going to collapse here, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:04.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Get up! Walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:06.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving you behind, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:09.55,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Then go...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.83,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:14.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:18.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I can't die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:22.94,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really going to go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:26.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Not joking, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:37.91,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you were going to go ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:41.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely don't want to die with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:45.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But you've got people waiting for you, too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:49.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you have the strength to talk, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:09:00.27,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,If only we had something to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:05.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know, Lin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:15.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Leather goods are edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:19.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Should be done by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:20.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:24.50,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have athlete's foot, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:27.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like I do, dumbass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:31.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:33.80,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.25,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:37.47,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't tried to save me back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:43.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing compared to the training I went through as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:46.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of annoying we don't know where we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:51.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,but we can search for the exit now that we've had our beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:53.16,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,An optimist, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:56.01,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just relentless about staying alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:10:00.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If I even thought about giving up,\NI'd get beaten and scolded by Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:06.97,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Something's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:09.93,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:13.21,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:15.26,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Envy, just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Please, tell us where the exit is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:20.37,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,That's pathetic, Edward Elric!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:23.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Humans would do anything to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:23.60,Default-alt,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:24.92,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:26.60,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,...there's no exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:24.24,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:24.92,Default-alt,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,You're despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:25.96,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.24,0:10:30.79,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You really had to do that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:33.52,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Even I got dragged in because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:35.99,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:38.53,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really inside Gluttony's stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:42.28,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,We're inside his stomach, and at the same time, we're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:44.15,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal ru-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:48.54,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Fullmetal Alchemist, shouldn't you have realized where we are by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:52.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,\Nwhen I was sucked in by Gluttony...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:54.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I recognize that sensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:56.78,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:59.63,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Since you've gone through it in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The Gate of Truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:14.98,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But this isn't how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:18.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It was all white, and there was a gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:21.47,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's how the real one is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:22.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,"Real"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:27.62,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Gluttony is the result of Father's unsuccessful attempt at recreating the Gate of Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:30.25,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What... did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:38.13,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,A poorly-made Gate of Truth that even Father couldn't get right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:42.88,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's safe to call this place the crevice between reality and the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:44.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The crevice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:48.29,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,There's no exit, nor a way to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:52.37,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do now is to wait until\Nthe span of our lives comes to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:54.02,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:57.07,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,...is wait until we die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:11.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No way in hell I'll let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:13.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw around with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:14.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Envy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:16.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:18.77,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,There's no exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.05,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to die here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:23.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:30.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If I die here, what will Al do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:33.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I promised him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:35.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I promised him we'd get our bodies back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:39.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:43.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is this Father guy that tried to recreate the Gate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:45.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Führer President Bradley?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:48.27,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Bradley?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:50.61,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Not even close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:52.62,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a Homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:54.86,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:58.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Research Laboratory 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:00.25,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Using people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:02.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Philosopher's stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:04.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:10.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If the Führer President is also a Homunculus, then that means it was you guys who started the Ishbal conflict...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.27,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Ishbal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:17.13,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,That was the most amusing task I'd ever been given!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:20.27,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what started that civil war in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:26.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, an army officer accidentally killed an Ishbalan child...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:27.83,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:31.83,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who shot the kid dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:57.02,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:14:02.54,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about Ishbal from Yoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:10.10,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,That felt amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:13.16,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Watching the civil war spread indefinitely from a single bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:16.66,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it was really refreshing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:18.79,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:26.97,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I disguised myself as a moderate officer who was against the military intervention of Ishbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:29.55,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Hear this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:34.56,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't even give an excuse for it and was sentenced to death by court-martial!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:39.74,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are so easy to manipulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:43.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:46.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The one who shot an innocent child dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:52.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The one who destroyed our hometown... The one who drove away the Ishbalans...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:55.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The one who created Scar, a vengeful murderer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:58.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The root cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:01.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...of what killed Winry's parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:04.69,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:09.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:11.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't give an inch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:14.26,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You brats want to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:16.01,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Ed, pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:24.40,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,We're all going to die here anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:27.82,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you something cool as a final gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:32.23,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Did you look beneath his feet when you were fighting him in the woods?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:33.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:37.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:40.90,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,He may not look like it, but he weighs quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:43.49,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,His true form must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:57.94,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:00.14,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:03.38,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,How could that be a Homunculus...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:06.48,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,An artificial human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:29.50,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:32.05,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,...should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:36.15,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:40.77,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do... I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:43.82,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get yelled at by Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:48.60,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Father? You have a dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:50.51,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:53.01,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The one who created the Homunculi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:54.90,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:02.96,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What happens to the mass you swallow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:04.73,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a trick to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:08.03,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Think... Think!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:11.03,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We decided we'd get our bodies back together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:13.63,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:19.47,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Gluttony, take me to your Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:23.27,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:27.60,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,You're a human sacrifice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:31.61,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, that's right. I'm a human sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:35.69,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck does he mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:43.42,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones currently confirmed as such are the Elric brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:46.07,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,What about Doctor Marcoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:47.43,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,You would think that it's about time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:48.88,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,There's Kimblee, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:53.26,Default,Guy4,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have the nerve to open the Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:58.97,Default,Guy4,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what about Mustang, the other sacrifice candidate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.52,0:18:03.94,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President wants to have a long chat with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:10.52,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you letting me live?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:14.42,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,To make you understand where you stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:19.41,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Since when has the military been beholden to the Homunculi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:24.34,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,It has been set up that way ever since this country was first reformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:29.17,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,So you've been smiling with glee, watching us struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:34.09,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Your hands that were shaking during Brigadier General Hughes' funeral...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:37.05,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Was that just an act?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:42.81,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone makes too big a deal out of the death of a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:48.96,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,They should have known his military uniform might become his burial attire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:56.87,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Brigadier General Hughes' daughter was so annoying during the funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.96,0:19:01.45,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,She really got on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:04.58,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, you also have a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.13,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:08.64,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Are you referring to Selim?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:11.38,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,He's a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:17.23,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how he'd react if he were to find out that his father, a man of utmost standing, is a Homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.55,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to blackmail me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:22.73,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,It is futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:27.47,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,He won't become my weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:30.48,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,But you're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:34.48,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,She'll become your weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:39.36,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Hawkeye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:41.63,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:44.49,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,Someone from the personnel bureau dropped by earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.94,0:19:48.80,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,I was transferred to Southern Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:51.20,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:52.75,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,Not just me, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:55.71,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,Second Lieutenant Breda was transferred to Western Headquarters,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:20:00.46,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,and Warrant Officer Falman was transferred to Northern Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:12.60,Default,Yako,0000,0000,0000,,You're Lieutenant Hawkeye, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:13.36,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:16.19,Default,Yako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yakovleff, from the personnel bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:17.96,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Personnel bureau...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:21.70,Default,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shtolhi, an assistant to the Führer President.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:23.65,Default,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:26.66,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a transfer order?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:28.00,Default,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:31.58,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me to review it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:37.42,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:40.75,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,What is with this insane personnel change?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:42.30,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you assigned?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:48.18,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,"Starting tomorrow, Lieutenant Riza Hawkeye will be stationed at Central Headquarters..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:52.28,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,"...as an assistant to the Führer President."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.51,0:20:55.31,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:58.31,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Roy Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:07.76,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,How delightful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:11.15,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, this isn't delightful at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:13.07,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Not the least bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:19.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:25.70,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:31.50,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.50,0:21:32.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:33.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We're in a sea of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:36.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There's plenty of iron here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:44.19,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,You have bad taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:47.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How so? I think it looks cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:53.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:54.90,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:56.58,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:22:00.43,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,And to top it off, that earlier attack broke a few of my ribs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:02.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:07.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't be satisfied until I give him a good beatdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.07,0:22:16.87,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Gluttony, are you sure we're going the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:17.44,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.04,0:22:21.27,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But this way... we're headed toward...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:26.44,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Your Father is in Central?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.25,0:24:02.39,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Is the soul acting in the shadows a guidepost to the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.15,0:24:05.33,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Fight, boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.33,0:24:09.46,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx96}if you are to see the truth and discover the depth of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.51,0:24:14.93,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.93,0:24:17.71,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 26, Reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.97,0:24:21.18,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say farewell...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.18,0:24:24.69,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...because I believe we'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.01,0:24:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
